angyang\",\"keyword\":\"Gantt Chart\",\"offcial\":\"1\",\"type\":\"extension\",\"site\":\"http:\\\/\\\/www.zentao.pm\",\"account\":\"ZenTaoALM\",\"addedTime\":\"2020-03-03 22:47:27\",\"updatedTime\":\"2020-03-03 23:19:43\",\"views\":\"2120\",\"downloads\":\"16\",\"grade\":\"0\",\"status\":\"released\",\"online\":\"1\",\"industry\":\"0\",\"color\":\"\",\"images\":\"\",\"snapStatus\":\"wait\",\"snapFaild\":\"\",\"snapedDate\":\"\",\"lang\":\"en\",\"langID\":\"139\",\"objectID\":\"47\",\"name\":\"Gantt Chart\",\"desc\":\"<p>This extension can view Gantt chart, and maintain task relations.<\\\/p>\\r\\n<p><br \\\/><\\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Gantt chart is one of robust features in ZenTao. It offers an intuitive view of the progress of the project. User can manage four types of task dependencies presented in ZenTao. Specific definitions of task dependencies can refer to the definition of Microsoft project&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\\/\\\/support.office.com\\\/en-us\\\/article\\\/Link-tasks-in-a-project-31b918ce-4b71-475c-9d6b-0ee501b4be57?ui=en-US&rs=en-US&ad=US\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"><strong>HERE<\\\/strong><\\\/a>.<\\\/p>\\r\\n<p><br \\\/><\\\/p>\",\"abstract\":\"Gantt chart feature in ZenTao.\",\"install\":\"<h4 style=\\\"color:#333333;\\\">1. Install through the buildin extension manager<\\\/h4>\\r\\n<span>1.1 Log in ZenTao as Administrator. Visit the Admin-&gt;Extension. <\\\/span><br \\\/><span>1.2 Go to the Get Extension page, search for this extension. <\\\/span><br \\\/><span>1.3 Click the AutoInstall and begin the installation. <\\\/span><br \\\/><br \\\/> \\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"color:#333333;\\\">2. Manual installation<\\\/h4>\\r\\n<span>Unzip this package and copy files under module directory to the zentao\\\/module.<\\\/span>\",\"viewLink\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.zentao.pm\\\/extension-viewExt-47-info-client.html\",\"stars\":0,\"latestRelease\":{\"score\":\"0\",\"public\":\"0\",\"lifePrice\":\"289.99\",\"charge\":1,\"downLink\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.zentao.pm\\\/extension-buyExt-32-download.html\",\"viewLink\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.zentao.pm\\\/extension-viewExt-47-releaseinfo-front-32.html\",\"md5\":\"1db010ec859e3ffb4ab980b516bef9ce\",\"releaseVersion\":\"3.5\",\"zentaoCompatible\":\"12.0\",\"depends\":\"\"}},\"45\":{\"id\":\"45\",\"category\":\"71\",\"code\":\"excel\",\"copyright\":\"EasyCorp\",\"author\":\"wangyidong\",\"keyword\":\"MS Excel, export\",\"offcial\":\"1\",\"type\":\"extension\",\"site\":\"http:\\\/\\\/www.zentao.pm\",\"account\":\"ZenTaoALM\",\"addedTime\":\"2020-03-03 21:29:53\",\"updatedTime\":\"2020-03-03 23:06:27\",\"views\":\"1883\",\"downloads\":\"10\",\"grade\":\"0\",\"status\":\"released\",\"online\":\"1\",\"industry\":\"0\",\"color\":\"\",\"images\":\"\",\"snapStatus\":\"wait\",\"snapFaild\":\"\",\"snapedDate\":\"\",\"lang\":\"en\",\"langID\":\"131\",\"objectID\":\"45\",\"name\":\"Excel Export\\\/Import\",\"desc\":\"<p>This extension is to export and import data in ZenTao as MS Excel file.<\\\/p>\\n<p><br \\\/><\\\/p>\\n<p>\\n  <p>With the help of the phpexcel class library, data in ZenTao can be exported as .xls files. Compared to the .csv format,&nbsp; xls files provide better format control and appearance.<\\\/p>\\n  <p><br \\\/>When exporting, select xlsx or xls format (if you need to export the images in the details, you can export the mht format file in the Professional version or the Enterprise version of ZenTao.<\\\/p>\\n  <p><br \\\/><\\\/p>\\n  <p>You can also use this extension to import Excel files. For more, refer to&nbsp;<span style=\\\"font-weight:700;\\\"><a href=\\\"\\\/book\\\/zentaopromanual\\\/free-open-source-project-management-software-excel-142.html\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">HERE<\\\/a><\\\/span>.<\\\/p>\\n<\\\/p>\",\"abstract\":\"Support for excel file export and import.\",\"install\":\"<h4>1. Install through the buildin extension manager<\\\/h4>\\n1.1 Log in ZenTao as Administrator. Visit the Admin-&gt;Extension. <br \\\/>\\n1.2 Go to the Get page, search for this extension. <br \\\/> 1.3